<HEADLINE> Asian Games Flag Relay Starts in Bangkok </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, September 6 (Xinhua) -- Thailand began the countdown
to this year's Asian Games as an across country flag relay
started from the Capital Bangkok on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The tournament's flag will be carried to cover a land of 76
regions in the country in a 9,099-kilometer relay which returns
to Bangkok on December 3.
</P>
<P>
The continental sports gala will be held in Bangkok from
December 6 to 20. 
</P>
