progress in the coming years under the leadership of the Workers'
Party of Korea headed by Kim Jong Il.
</P>
<P>
Hu noted that China and DPRK are friendly neighbors linked by
mountains and rivers, and that Sino-DPRK friendship, established
and fostered by the older generations of leaders of the two
countries, has withstood the test of history and has therefore
rooted in the hearts of the two peoples.
</P>
<P>
