and aspiration of the two peoples, and will also serve regional
peace and stability.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese Communist Party, government and people highly value
the Sino-DPRK friendship, and will continue their efforts to
further such friendship.
</P>
<P>
Song Pong Hwan highly praised DPRK-China friendship and thanked
the Chinese government, Party and people for their support for the
socialist construction of DPRK and its cause of national
reunification.
</P>
<P>
Chinese foreign minister Tang Jiaxuan and the Chief of the
General Staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army Fu Quanyou
were among the guests at the banquet.  
