<HEADLINE> Blair Urges European Aerospace Industry to Restructure </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, September 7 (Xinhua) -- British Prime Minister Tony
Blair Monday stressed the urgent need for the European aerospace
industry to undertake restructuring.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the opening ceremony of the Farnborough
International Air Show, Blair said: "Over the last year, the
(European) aerospace industry has made important progress on
restructuring in order to beat the growing challenge of being
globally competitive.
</P>
