<HEADLINE> Maputo International Fair Attracts More </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, September 6 (Xinhua) -- Maputo managed a better
international trade fair this year over that of last year, with
10,000 more visitors and two more foreign countries participating
in the fair, an organization officer said here Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Amerrico Magaia, director-general of the Maputo International
Fair, an annual trade fair in the country, said about 170
companies, including firms from 11 foreign countries came to the
fair.
</P>
