Last year nine foreign countries sent their companies to the
fair.
</P>
<P>
About 46 companies from China made their debut in the trade
fair. The companies have come from China's Anhui, Fujian,
Guangdong and Hebei Provinces.
</P>
<P>
The trade fair attracted enterprises involved in industry,
tourism, agriculture, food-processing, computer and insurance.
